German Light Vehicle Sales in U.S. Rise 18% in May, VDA Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-06-02T14:26:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/german-light-vehicle-sales-in-u-s-rise-18-in-may-vda-says.html
German light vehicle sales on the
U.S. market rose 18 percent in May to more than 90,600 units,
the VDA carmakers lobby group said today in an e-mailed
statement.  The market share of German carmakers increased 0.2 percent
to 7.6 percent, VDA said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at   arummer@bloomberg.net  